column5: havn't posted in a while, i'll b e at the ganny all weekend. cheers.
Good luck to you too!  I'll be out there...somewhere....hopefully catching something other than a cold.
Thanks.I will be out with my son on Lake Massawippi,Quebec first time out with the boat.Supposed to rain like hell we will be dressed for that.  Good Luck to All.MTP

Thank you.....  Best of luck??????  Somewhere back in my life I started to look at it as ---  - 1/3 being experience - 1/3 being hope - 1/3 being luck  carp-starter - in any case, good luck to all. I will be going out on Monday or Tuesday to avoid seeing all the crap that I would see on the weekend.
